item.title: i am incompetent
item.description: today I got up late for work again. it is stupid. I recently oredered a new alarm clock. it is a sony sleep machine. but it doesn’t get me up. I just sleep through the alarm. so if I forget to set my phone to ring.. I won’t ever get up. I hate it. I need to replace my new alarm clock with my old one. my old one is super sketchy too.
